{
  "texts": [
    "For the CRISPR-Cas9 screens and mutagenesis assay, we generated isogenic clonal RAD18 -/-and RAD18 +/+ cell lines by transducing parental U373 cells with a RAD18-directed sgRNA or with a non-targeting sgRNA respectively.",
    "In brief, a LentiCRISPRv2-DD-Cas9-BSD vector (generated inhouse, DD: destabilizing domain 79, Supplementary Fig. 10) encoding sgRAD18 or a non-targeting sgRNA was transduced into U373 cells by electroporation.",
    "Transfected cells were selected by growth in blasticidin (BSD, 10 µg/mL) for 4 days and then additionally treated with Shield-1 (1 µM) for another 6 days.",
    "Single clones of blasticidin-resistant and Shield-1-treated cells were isolated, expanded and tested for RAD18 disruption by TIDE assay (https://tide.nki.nl/) and western blot.",
    "The clonal U373 RAD18 -/-and RAD18 +/+ cell lines thus obtained were verified lentivirus cassette-free based upon blasticidin-sensitivity."
  ]
}